snippet.title: Official Sea of Thieves Bilge Rat Adventures: Festival of the Damned
snippet.description:
Burn brightly to celebrate your friendly neighbourhood Ferryman in this new Bilge Rat Adventure, Festival of the Damned. It all begins on October 31st! Learn more about the Bilge Rats at https://www.seaofthieves.com/game/the-bilge-rats

Buy the game and forge your own legend: https://www.xbox.com/seaofthieves
Dive into the Sea of Thieves Forums: https://www.seaofthieves.com/forum
Follow Sea of Thieves on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SeaOfThieves
Like Sea of Thieves on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SeaOfThievesGame
Watch Sea of Thieves on Mixer: https://mixer.com/SeaOfThieves
Talk Sea of Thieves on Discord: https://discord.gg/seaofthieves

Xbox Live Gold required to play on Xbox One (sold separately).
